{"tid":2112821,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"沙田警署廚師檢測呈陰性 食堂周日重開","createTime":"2020-07-17T15:14:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T04:30:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"5ac28002c79d22473c7b0b2d0cd5106e685babc2","tid":2112821,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:14:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200717/TGGZCAT5OGYJUS5CWWTEPZ55CY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200717%2FTGGZCAT5OGYJUS5CWWTEPZ55CY%2F&d=6SBmejzB2pOSQzgprEhHpYleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=64f9542a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200717%2FTGGZCAT5OGYJUS5CWWTEPZ55CY%2F&h=49e15678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200717/TGGZCAT5OGYJUS5CWWTEPZ55CY/</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭政府日前禁止食肆晚市堂食，但警署食堂卻獲豁免執行，未料即有警署食堂人員疑感染武漢肺炎。《蘋果》獲悉，沙田警署食堂一名廚師近日發燒，正等候深喉唾液測試結果，沙田警署食堂昨起暫停營業。<br />\n<br />\n警方晚上回覆查詢，指該名食堂職員經初步測試後，對武漢肺炎病毒呈陰性反應，食堂將於7月19日（周日）恢復服務。"},{"pid":"e65388ca8489a6be0b051a56a5b9936cbc52439f","tid":2112821,"uid":89517,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:15:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8741804ea88282762a8e8f03aca8752b49589545","tid":2112821,"uid":183576,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T15:15:33.000Z","msg":"集氣係假陰性<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" cl